{"article_id":"HpyeQZPIPeIGjsW3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"LONDON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"British Prime Minister David Cameron said Monday","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that he will resign by Wednesday ,","depth":10},{"id":3,"text":"paving the way for Home Secretary Theresa May","depth":12},{"id":4,"text":"to succeed him","depth":12},{"id":5,"text":"as the United Kingdom 's second female leader .","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"Cameron 's announcement came","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"just hours after May 's only competitor for Conservative Party leader and prime minister","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"- Energy Minister Andrea Leadsom -","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"dropped out of the running .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"U.K. 's next prime minister , Theresa May , formidable like 'Iron Lady ' Thatcher Graham Brady ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"who leads the committee","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"overseeing the election of the new Conservative leader ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"May was confirmed by the panel .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Speaking to supporters after the latest political twists and turns ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"May said","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"she is \" honored and humbled \" to be chosen as the new leader .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Leadsom said","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"she did not believe","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"she had sufficient support within the party","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to lead a strong and stable government .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Party lawmakers last week narrowed the choice of candidates for leader to May and Leadsom .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Cameron had announced","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"he would resign by October","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"shortly after the June 23 referendum supported a U.K. exit , or Brexit , from the 28-nation European Union .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Cameron led the campaign","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to remain in the EU .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"May ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"who also supported remaining in the EU ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"won 199 votes Thursday from party lawmakers ,","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"while Leadsom ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"who backed the campaign","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"to leave ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"had 84 .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" Brexit means Brexit ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"and we ' re going to make a success of it , \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"May said Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"as she promised to deliver \" a strong , new positive vision for the future of our country . \"","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"She did elaborate on her plans","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"for pursuing the formal split with the EU .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Leadsom , 53 , apologized to May on Monday","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"after suggesting in an interview with the Times of London","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"that being a mother made her a better candidate for prime minister than May ,","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"who has no children .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Last week , Leadsom denied embellishing her resume regarding her 25-year career in finance","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"following media reports","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"that she had done so .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Theresa May :","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"5 things","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"to know about likely new U.K. leader","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"May , 59 , will become the U.K. 's first female prime minister since Margaret Thatcher ,","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"known as the `` Iron Lady , ''","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"governed from 1979 to 1990 .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Thatcher died in 2013 .","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"Boris Johnson , a leading `` leave '' campaigner and former London mayor , was the favorite","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"to replace Cameron ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"but dropped out of the leadership race","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"after a close colleague claimed","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"he lacked leadership skills for the top post .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Johnson then gave May his backing .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"`` Theresa May will provide the authority and the leadership","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"necessary to unite the Conservative party","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and take the country forward in the coming weeks and months , ''","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Johnson said in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Tim Loughton , Leadsom 's campaign manager , accused some Conservative Party members and journalists of making `` an onslaught of often very personal attacks '' against her .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"`` Using spin and underhand tactics against decent people","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"whose prime motivation is to serve","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"has for too long undermined the confidence of the public in our politics , ''","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"The new leader was originally scheduled to be chosen by 150,000 Conservative Party members on Sept. 9 .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":141,"left":0,"right":140,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":140,"left":117,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":110,"right":116,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":92,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":91,"right":22,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":91,"left":84,"right":90,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":84,"left":79,"right":83,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":75,"right":78,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":1,"right":74,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":74,"left":2,"right":73,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"